Program
  Procedures:
    Procedure p
      Assignment
        Identifier(b)
        BinaryOp(+)
          Identifier(a)
          Number(3)
  Main:
    Read
      Identifier(n)
    For(i TO)
      From:
        Number(1)
      To:
        Identifier(n)
    Do
      ProcCall(p)
        Identifier(n)
        Identifier(i)
    Write
      Identifier(n)
